title: Kayn/Jayce Bug

embed.description: Was just playing a league game as Kayn and when I w'd a Jayce an interesting thing happened. LOL Add me on League at TAB Disaster

body: I was just playing a normal Nexus Blitz game as Kayn {{champion:141}} and as Jayce {{champion:126}} used his ability I w'd and he got launched skyward. {{sticker:sg-lux-2}}

Looks fine and working as intended. :)
